\(\mathcal{H}_{T}=\pi _{\~{\Phi }}\.{\~{\Phi }}+\pi _{\~{\theta }}\.{\~{\theta }}_{T}-\mathcal{L}^{(2)}+\lambda _{1}\mathcal{C}_{1}\)
